            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onion is cooking, boil a kettle</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 200ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [260ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [340ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>green lentils</strong></p>",
