      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>carrot, bay leaf[ves]</strong>,<strong> drained green lentils </strong>and <strong>vegetable stock</strong> to the pan</p><p>Cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until the carrots are tender, stirring occasionally – this is your <strong>lentil stew</strong></p>",
