    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, zest half your <strong>lemon[s]</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining non-zested lemon</strong> into wedges</p><p>Chop your<strong> parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks (save some leaves for garnish!)</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
