            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>cod fillets</strong> to an oiled baking tray and top with the lemon <strong>breadcrumb mixture</strong></p><p>Once the stew has 10 min left, put the tray in the oven for 10-12 min or until the breadcrumbs are golden and the cod is cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
