    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the carrots are tender, squeeze in the juice of the <strong>zested lemon</strong></p><p>Add a knob of <strong>butter </strong>and season with a good grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> lemon-crusted cod</strong> over the <strong>lentil stew</strong> and garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge </strong> and the <strong>reserved parsley leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
